But there are others solutions one is Nomad.
It&rsquo;s made by Hashicorp, creators of Vault, Consul, Terraform&hellip;
In general Hashicorp is synonym with quality.
Nomad is a task scheduler, a task could be execute a command, run a Docker container or a QEMU vm&hellip;
